{"id": "1423941553302409258", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一**\n棺材里爬出的轮盘赌，雪夜里穷追不舍的过去。\n开一局，再一局，狼的皮毛和好运气，会带来一个阳光明媚的下周一。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Ryker EP· Next Lucky Monday\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Ryker EP· Next Lucky Monday**\nThe roulette wheel grinds its way out of the coffin; the past still hounds through the snowy night.\nGame after game... The Wolf's warm pelt and good fortune will surely bring the next sunny Monday.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:55:21.862000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Showoff", "emoji_id": "1400771654199541850", "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1423941553742680204", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2295127, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423941553742680204/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69cccf69&is=69cb7de9&hm=905ba32bee39e2bd052f9a947daa0f53f844602130669d4d7b6493ebe39913f2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423941800623865927", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 坏牌-Bad Hands-**\n\n可怜的、狂妄的、不知天高地厚的狼。\n他和其他客人一起被扔在了休息室，在一场短暂安宁的赌局里。\n失去了习以为常的好运气，他输掉了超过一万雷欧坊。\n\nThe poor, conceited, reckless wolf.\nHe was trapped in the lounge with the other guests, for a moment of peaceful gambling.\nHis usual luck was somehow gone, and in that game, he lost over ten thousand Leonian Florin.", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:56:20.828000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423941800019890197", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1374053, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423941800019890197/1.jpg?ex=69cccfa4&is=69cb7e24&hm=d156c0f7703fc5fa836553cc5ed79e85c5cbe82f5826a1c3627d41ebc3beb2ba&"}, {"id": "1423941800413888583", "filename": "01._-Bad_Hands-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20162096, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423941800413888583/01._-Bad_Hands-.wav?ex=69cccfa4&is=69cb7e24&hm=6c58dc310b0c91600927a5f9a693f8968a649e793c2c63008a1c7936022a5d66&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423941857087590452", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 小小的N-The Tiny \"N\"-**\n\n一样的礼帽，一样的玫瑰，一样的笑声。\n帷幕已经拉起，观众已经就位，来吧，来吧，来找一找，凶手是从黑雾中掉出的哪一位？\n\nSame hat, same rose, same laugh.\nThe curtain's drawn, the audience's in place. Come and find out which one, emerging from the fading black fog, is the murderer?", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:56:34.290000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423941856277823488", "filename": "02._N-The_Tiny_N-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 14870102, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423941856277823488/02._N-The_Tiny_N-.wav?ex=69cccfb2&is=69cb7e32&hm=b9ab948fea7d97b5e07b09f010072e686c22048e0daa36f6f12441968537e983&"}, {"id": "1423941856818892891", "filename": "2N.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1383942, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423941856818892891/2N.jpg?ex=69cccfb2&is=69cb7e32&hm=5af8c21188aec5393eaf6542ff127af27ae8468e73010ace5239002111b0c357&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423942024813608991", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 嗅觉-Beast's Scent-**\n\n极寒，诡计，大雪，全都扰乱不了野兽的嗅觉。\nFreeze, tricks, heavy snow—none of it can foil the beast's keen nose.", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:57:14.279000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423942023186092154", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1379323, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942023186092154/3.jpg?ex=69cccfd9&is=69cb7e59&hm=d2d43ae5dc8f20cadd9b6489c8d495898bca2ece834d89fb7d251bb1e207a42d&"}, {"id": "1423942024100319342", "filename": "03._-Beasts_Scent-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19118102, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942024100319342/03._-Beasts_Scent-.wav?ex=69cccfda&is=69cb7e5a&hm=ed0f2ed1e89ee028108a70d7bf88ec92c6fa7feb473a56563a72dbe3759d2321&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423942160524382309", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 抓住你了-Got You-**\n\n有一位小姐的手臂被伸缩绳串起，有一位小姐和另一位死掉两次的小姐一起，制造出了一个虚假的亡魂。\n\nOne lady has an arm fitted with a retractable link rope. Another lady, along with the lady who died twice, conjured a false ghost.", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:57:46.635000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423942159735853097", "filename": "04._-Got_You-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20010358, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942159735853097/04._-Got_You-.wav?ex=69cccffa&is=69cb7e7a&hm=8177c9e5258cd6361e2026dbc723065d3b8245eb5184d69c1560dab97ec5d844&"}, {"id": "1423942160310599761", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1387359, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942160310599761/4.jpg?ex=69cccffa&is=69cb7e7a&hm=137b8e556d48d7bb010038641bcc1c9228b5d5bf253da413fd2711fb8428583a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423942280330346507", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05. 拷贝恶习-The Vice-**\n\n给予叛逆者以宠溺，祂恶趣味的牺牲品，也分享了祂的恶习。\nIndulged with His favor, the rebel, the victim of His wicked taste, also shares His vice.", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:58:15.199000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423942279495684136", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1391816, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942279495684136/5.jpg?ex=69ccd017&is=69cb7e97&hm=552f31f2943031b20f2b1ce786350a3b9f1d5b74a8af5478fa17cebcc49402c8&"}, {"id": "1423942279890206720", "filename": "05._-The_Vice-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 9539452, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942279890206720/05._-The_Vice-.wav?ex=69ccd017&is=69cb7e97&hm=e2988e0b9a54d2d36daba307c1c9165ac13c9b97cdd23c61011e356360c84600&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423942425403064372", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06. 名侦探的梭哈-Detective's All-In-**\n\n不不不不不不不，梭哈不是为了赢。\n梭哈的重点就是梭哈，梭哈就是为了梭哈。\n\nNuh-uh. All-in isn't about the win!\nThe point of all-in lies in the act itself; all-in is all about all-in.", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:58:49.787000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423942424807342141", "filename": "06._-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19810354, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942424807342141/06._-.wav?ex=69ccd039&is=69cb7eb9&hm=5851bc1975a4d566c460fd9a2a723b46dba35efa5e1ec78c30c85fd528e8d82a&"}, {"id": "1423942425382096936", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1402601, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942425382096936/6.jpg?ex=69ccd039&is=69cb7eb9&hm=118362cf9c6e843e0499b45a4ff26b4d64204856534ce6b08ccc3e757cfc6843&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1423942691191787643", "channel_id": "1423941553302409258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07. 哦，生活-C'est La Vie-**\n\n好的日常总是要由噩梦开始，在墓园结束。\n哦，这就是生活，甜美的生活。\n\nA good day always starts with a nightmare, and ends in the graveyard.\nOh, this is life, my friend. Taste the bitter honey.", "timestamp": "2025-10-04T07:59:53.156000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423942690373894194", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1384399, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942690373894194/7.jpg?ex=69ccd078&is=69cb7ef8&hm=4b34a29f14be5c3220b387db5d088b7709c43c8f17e8181e2590ac0dca1c359e&"}, {"id": "1423942690701181009", "filename": "07._-Cest_La_Vie-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 50050354, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423941553302409258/1423942690701181009/07._-Cest_La_Vie-.wav?ex=69ccd079&is=69cb7ef9&hm=354a8ce36b01c84e4fa62b00b03218fd18c5ddd8f9b0f1bafe9568cd4390ce3a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423941553302409258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：莱克 EP·狼的下周一", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
